    <a href="https://squarespace.pxf.io/stackpick" class="cta-button" rel="nofollow sponsored">Try Squarespace Commerce →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tool-card" id="wix-ecommerce">
    <h3>#4 Wix eCommerce — $17/mo</h3>
    <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Small businesses wanting easy drag-and-drop store building</p>
    <p><strong>Why switch from WooCommerce:</strong> Most intuitive drag-and-drop builder</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unlimited products</li>
